snippet.title: Destroy (滅), 1989, Fighting, SoftStar
snippet.description: One of the oldest game by Taiwanese company SoftStar. The developer is DOMO. This is simple fighting using one-to-one formula. You will save your girl, she is captured and kept in the castle. The gameplay is very hard and saving procedures were not provided by developers.
